# OpenClaw Cron 配置文件

**位置：** `~/.openclaw/config/cron.json` 或工作区 `cron/cron-config.json`

---

## 谋士天团定时任务配置

```json
{
  "version": "1.0",
  "timezone": "Asia/Shanghai",
  "tasks": {
    "office-status-update": {
      "name": "Office 实时数据更新",
      "description": "每 5 分钟更新 Office 页面 Agent 状态数据",
      "schedule": "*/5 * * * *",
      "command": "powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File \"C:\\Users\\JINDA\\.openclaw\\workspace-zhugeliang\\cron\\update-office-status.ps1\"",
      "cwd": "C:\\Users\\JINDA\\.openclaw\\workspace-zhugeliang\\website",
      "enabled": true,
      "timeout": 60,
      "log": true,
      "logFile": "C:\\Users\\JINDA\\.openclaw\\logs\\office-status-update.log"
    },
    
    "agent-activity-report": {
      "name": "Agent 活动状态上报",
      "description": "每 2 分钟各 Agent 自动上报活动状态",
      "schedule": "*/2 * * * *",
      "command": "powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File \"C:\\Users\\JINDA\\.openclaw\\workspace-zhugeliang\\cron\\auto-report-activity.ps1\"",
      "cwd": "C:\\Users\\JINDA\\.openclaw\\workspace-zhugeliang\\website",
      "enabled": true,
      "timeout": 30,
      "log": true
    },
    
    "hourly-summary": {
      "name": "每小时任务汇总",
      "description": "整点生成任务汇总报告",
      "schedule": "0 * * * *",
      "command": "powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File \"C:\\Users\\JINDA\\.openclaw\\workspace-zhugeliang\\cron\\hourly-summary.ps1\"",
      "cwd": "C:\\Users\\JINDA\\.openclaw\\workspace-zhugeliang",
      "enabled": true,
      "timeout": 120,
      "log": true
    }
  }
}
```

